mones Idees]]\n| lyrics10        = Smaroula Maragoudaki\n| music10         = Spiros Georgiou\n| length10        = 3:22\n| title11         = Zisame\n| note11          = featuring Dionysis Shoinas\n| extra11         = [[To Kati]]\n| lyrics11        = Phoebus\n| music11         = Phoebus\n| length11        = 3:27\n| title12         = Entalma Syllipseos\n| note12          = \n| extra12         = [[Endalma Silepseos]]\n| lyrics12        = Nikos Vaxavanelis\n| music12         = Andreas Mexas\n| length12        = 1:15\n| title13         = Atofio Hrysafi\n| note13          = \n| extra13         = [[Atofio Hrysafi]]\n| lyrics13        = Phoebus\n| music13         = Phoebus\n| length13        = 2:00\n| title14         = Ksypoliti Horevo\n| note14          = \n| extra14         = [[Atofio Hrysafi]]\n| lyrics14        = Kostas Tournas\n| music14         = Kostas Tournas\n| length14        = 2:19\n| title15         = Mi Me Sygkrineis\n| note15          = \n| extra15         = [[Atofio Hrysafi]]\n| lyrics15        = Kostas Tournas\n| music15         = Kostas Tournas\n| length15        = 3:12\n| title16         = Stigmes\n| note16          = featuring Kostas Tournas\n| extra16         = [[Apla Ta Pragmata]]\n| lyrics16        = Kostas Tournas\n| music16         = Kostas Tournas\n| length16        = 4:05\n| title17         = Oti Oneirevomaste Ginetai\n| note17          = featuring Kostas Tournas\n| extra17         = [[Atofio Hrysafi]]\n| lyrics17        = Kostas Tournas\n| music17         = Kostas Tournas\n| length17        = 2:34\n| title18         = Eho Sta Matia Ourano\n| note18          = \n| extra18         = [[Eho Sta Matia Ourano]]\n| lyrics18        = Vasilis Giannopoulos\n| music18         = Christos Dantis \n| length18        = 2:06\n}}\n\n{{tracklist\n| headline        = Disc three\n| extra_column    = Original album\n| title1          = Doro Theou\n| note1           = \n| extra1          = [[Doro Theou]]\n| lyrics1         = Yioula Georgiou\n| music1          = [[Giorgo